						<p>Śaka 1466, Pramādīcha, Āni 3. [Irregular] = c. 16th Century.</p>						

						<p>The trustees of the temple and the nāḍu decided to honour the Nine <hi rend="italic">nagarattār</hi> with a golden fillet on the day of the swinging festival in appreciation of the latter's renovation work of the <hi rend="italic">tiruvūñjal-maṇḍapam.</hi></p>						

